import React from 'react'
import { Form,Row,Button,Col} from 'react-bootstrap';
const Formb = () => {
  return (
    <>
 <Form>
  <Row>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control placeholder="First name" />
    </Col>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control placeholder="Last name" />
    </Col>
  </Row>
</Form>

  <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
    Submit
  </Button>

    </>
  )
}

export default Formb
